# Berserker
Berserkers are the rage machine of the battle field. For most combatants, the battlefield is a frietening place, but the *Berserker* thrives and feeds off the chaos. While most are scared or overcome their fear of battle though courage or sheer will power, the Berserker is completely at home in it.

The more they deal damage and the more  they take, the stronger they become and the harder they are to stop.

